				<p class="mb-4">Nature Near Me is a web application that provides:</p>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
					<li>Interactive maps showing earthquakes, wildlife sightings, and natural features</li>
					<li>Real-time data from USGS, eBird, and other nature data sources</li>
					<li>Weather information and national park details</li>
					<li>Educational content about local nature and geology</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
