					<li>You may not copy, modify, or distribute our content without permission</li>
					<li>Educational and personal use is generally permitted</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">Nature Near Me and its operators are not liable for:</p>
