				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">10. Governing Law</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">These terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction where Nature Near Me operates. Any disputes will be resolved in accordance with applicable law.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-8">
